ation in the Late Roman Republic, the Emperor Nero's canal project and its failure, and the shifting growth of the Roman settlement in the territory"--From publisher's website.  aDescription based on information from the publisher. 0aRomanszGreecezCorinth RegionxHistory. 0aCorinth Region (Greece)xHistory. 0aCorinth, Isthmus of (Greece)xHistory. 0aCorinth Region (Greece)xHistory, Naval. 0aCorinth Region (Greece)xCommercexHistory. 0aCorinth Region (Greece)xAntiquities. 0aGreecexHistoryy146 B.C.-323 A.D. 0aMediterranean RegionxHistoryyTo 476. 4aElectronic books.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)epublisher.40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.5074123